Q: Which controls help Australian small businesses mitigate phishing or scam-related cyber threats?

Cypher used:
 MATCH (h:Entity)-[r:RELATION]->(t:Entity)
WHERE toLower(h.name) CONTAINS 'controls' OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS 'controls' OR toLower(h.name) CONTAINS 'phishing' OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS 'phishing' OR toLower(h.name) CONTAINS 'scam' OR toLower(t.name) CONTAINS 'scam'
RETURN h.name AS head, r.type AS relation, t.name AS tail
LIMIT 25

