  - Phishing/targeted malicious emails --RELATED_TO--> Top concern of SMBs
  - SMBs that experienced cyber-attacks --RELATED_TO--> Phishing (most prevalent type)
  - Malware, Phishing and Ransomware --RELATED_TO--> Most commonly understood cyber security risks (among SMBs)
  - Lack of competence (in employees) --CAUSES--> Vulnerability to social engineering attacks like phishing

