lementing financial controls is a control that can help mitigate phishing or scam-related cyber threats.  Phishing --RELATED_TO--> Top concern of SMBs.  Therefore, implementing email filtering controls is a control that can help mitigate phishing or scam-related cyber threats.  Phishing/targeted malicious emails --RELATED_TO--> Top concern of SMBs.  Therefore, implementing email authentication controls is a control that can help mitigate phishing or scam-related cyber threats.  Phishing --RELATED_TO--> Malware/Ransomware (common understood risks).  Therefore, implementing security updates and patches is a control that can help mitigate phishing or scam-related cyber threats.



